1
00:00:02,040 --> 00:00:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I apologize for the wait.</font>

2
00:00:07,290 --> 00:00:09,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You even had a change of clothes for me.</font>

3
00:00:09,830 --> 00:00:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you so much.</font>

4
00:00:11,750 --> 00:00:13,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Have you made up your mind?</font>

5
00:00:14,460 --> 00:00:15,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes.</font>

6
00:00:15,670 --> 00:00:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Pride, who was it
that saved me from the pub?</font>

7
00:00:21,540 --> 00:00:22,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Val!</font>

8
00:00:22,830 --> 00:00:25,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Come over here, right now!</font>

9
00:00:25,130 --> 00:00:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What?! Get off my back!</font>

10
00:00:27,290 --> 00:00:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You don't need me for anything!</font>

11
00:00:29,830 --> 00:00:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Whoa, Mistress!</font>

12
00:00:31,380 --> 00:00:35,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You shoulda told me
when the pretty boy woke up!</font>

13
00:00:35,130 --> 00:00:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Damn it!</font>

14
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:48,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Cuz this is what happens!</font>

15
00:00:48,420 --> 00:00:50,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, that's right.</font>

16
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:51,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I gave him permission to ignore decorum,</font>

17
00:00:51,880 --> 00:00:54,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">but only while he was
keeping an eye on Leon.</font>

18
00:00:55,080 --> 00:00:59,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">At any other time, he's bound to show
deference by the fealty contract.</font>

19
00:01:01,290 --> 00:01:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It was you?</font>

20
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:09,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you very much
for everything you've done.</font>

21
00:01:09,630 --> 00:01:12,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I don't know what would have
become of me without your help.</font>

22
00:01:13,580 --> 00:01:16,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I will make sure
to repay you for this kindness.</font>

23
00:01:17,420 --> 00:01:21,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No, I didn't choose to do it.</font>

24
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I was ordered to by my mistress!</font>

25
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:28,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hey, Mistress!</font>

26
00:01:28,420 --> 00:01:29,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Gimme a break already!</font>

27
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You have permission
to ignore decorum with Prince Leon.</font>

28
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:36,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I only saved you
'cause my mistress ordered me to.</font>

29
00:01:36,830 --> 00:01:38,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Couldn't give a crap what happens to you!</font>

30
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:41,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That doesn't matter.</font>

31
00:01:42,250 --> 00:01:46,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You saved me, and that fact is undeniable.</font>

32
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I truly am grateful to you.</font>

33
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:54,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And thank you to you two, as well.</font>

34
00:01:55,250 --> 00:01:57,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll make sure to repay you in kind.</font>

35
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:04,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now that's a genuine smile, right?</font>

36
00:02:06,750 --> 00:02:09,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let's go to the castle.</font>

37
00:02:34,580 --> 00:02:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Tatta ichido kiri darake no kyou o</font>

38
00:02:37,330 --> 00:02:39,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Mudatsukai shiten na yo</font>

39
00:02:39,580 --> 00:02:42,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Tadashisa nante mon wa sa</font>

40
00:02:42,420 --> 00:02:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Dareka ni totte tsugou no ii risouron</font>

41
00:02:46,170 --> 00:02:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Atama no oku de kikoeru koe ni</font>

42
00:02:48,750 --> 00:02:51,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Madowasareten na yo</font>

43
00:02:51,130 --> 00:02:54,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Futa akerya karappo nanda kitto</font>

44
00:02:54,670 --> 00:02:57,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kokoro no ugoku mama ni ikite</font>

45
00:02:57,630 --> 00:03:02,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kodoku mo oikosenai kurai no speed de</font>

46
00:03:02,670 --> 00:03:06,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Dareka ni totte no risou o michibiki dasu made</font>

47
00:03:08,460 --> 00:03:11,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Ima, nanimo kamo o seotte</font>

48
00:03:11,330 --> 00:03:14,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kawaranai koto sae utagatte</font>

49
00:03:14,250 --> 00:03:16,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Mukuwarenai nara mukuwareru made</font>

50
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:19,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Yamenakerya ii</font>

51
00:03:20,130 --> 00:03:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Mada, dekiru koto ga arun nara</font>

52
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:25,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Mirai o torikaese yo</font>

53
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Daremo shiranai kotae ni tadoritsukeru made</font>

54
00:03:31,710 --> 00:03:35,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Ima, nando demo taguriyosete miseru</font>

55
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:45,000
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}The Cruel Queen Makes a Declaration</b></font>

56
00:03:42,130 --> 00:03:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I do apologize for the sudden visit,</font>

57
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:47,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Your Majesty, King Gregorio.</font>

58
00:03:48,170 --> 00:03:50,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Please excuse my intrusion.</font>

59
00:03:52,380 --> 00:03:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I would like to explain to you
the events leading up to now,</font>

60
00:03:57,210 --> 00:04:00,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">but before that,
I have one request to make.</font>

61
00:04:01,330 --> 00:04:07,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Will you please summon Prince Erwin
and Prince Homer to join us right now?</font>

62
00:04:07,460 --> 00:04:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I would really like to see them.</font>

63
00:04:09,710 --> 00:04:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, as it happens...</font>

64
00:04:11,790 --> 00:04:16,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm sure my sons would love to meet
with Leon's fiancée.</font>

65
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:17,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh my.</font>

66
00:04:17,630 --> 00:04:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Don't get the wrong idea, Your Majesty.</font>

67
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:22,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">As it currently stands,</font>

68
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I am not here as his fiancée,
but as a representative of the queen.</font>

69
00:04:28,210 --> 00:04:33,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I received official permission
from my mother to make this visit.</font>

70
00:04:35,790 --> 00:04:37,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I will ask you once more.</font>

71
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:45,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Please bring Prince Erwin
and Prince Homer here.</font>

72
00:04:46,500 --> 00:04:47,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Elder Brother!</font>

73
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:49,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're home safe!</font>

74
00:04:52,130 --> 00:04:54,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It is an honor to meet the both of you,</font>

75
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:57,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Prince Erwin and Prince Homer.</font>

76
00:04:57,670 --> 00:05:03,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you for taking excellent care
of my darling fiancé.</font>

77
00:05:08,830 --> 00:05:11,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">By the way, Your Majesty...</font>

78
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:14,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Before we get down to business,</font>

79
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:18,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I know Leon has something to say
about his situation.</font>

80
00:05:21,750 --> 00:05:22,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Father.</font>

81
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:27,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Last night, I woke up sitting at a pub
in town and unable to move,</font>

82
00:05:27,170 --> 00:05:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">but Pride saved me
before anyone noticed.</font>

83
00:05:29,380 --> 00:05:33,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It was all part of a plot
by Erwin and Homer to frame me.</font>

84
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:36,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They came to my room
and made me drink spiked wine,</font>

85
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">then abandoned me at the pub.</font>

86
00:05:40,210 --> 00:05:41,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wait a minute, Leon!</font>

87
00:05:41,830 --> 00:05:44,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I think there's been a misunderstanding!</font>

88
00:05:44,210 --> 00:05:46,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Homer is right!</font>

89
00:05:46,290 --> 00:05:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We only insisted
on sharing some wine last night</font>

90
00:05:50,210 --> 00:05:52,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">because we were sad to part ways with you.</font>

91
00:05:52,420 --> 00:05:55,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But we'd never spike it!
That's just a wild accusation!</font>

92
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:57,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Except it's not.</font>

93
00:05:57,830 --> 00:06:00,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Pride's subordinates
rescued me from the pub.</font>

94
00:06:00,790 --> 00:06:04,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They determined that I had been drugged.</font>

95
00:06:04,710 --> 00:06:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, that proves nothing!</font>

96
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's all just rubbish
cooked up by Princess Pride!</font>

97
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Kingdom of Freesia
is trying to pull the wool over your eyes!</font>

98
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He's right!</font>

99
00:06:15,710 --> 00:06:18,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Freesia has been buttering you up,
Elder Brother.</font>

100
00:06:18,670 --> 00:06:22,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now they're painting us
in a bad light with this nonsense</font>

101
00:06:22,210 --> 00:06:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">to give them an excuse
to declare war on our nation!</font>

102
00:06:25,330 --> 00:06:26,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I guarantee it!</font>

103
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:30,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I mean,
it hardly seems like a coincidence</font>

104
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:32,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">they somehow found you
just in the nick of time, right?</font>

105
00:06:32,500 --> 00:06:34,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's painfully obvious.</font>

106
00:06:34,250 --> 00:06:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Kingdom of Freesia
has fabricated this entire thing,</font>

107
00:06:37,330 --> 00:06:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">either by hiring someone
to do the kidnapping,</font>

108
00:06:39,130 --> 00:06:42,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">or even just convincing you
to play along, Elder Brother.</font>

109
00:06:44,380 --> 00:06:46,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Erwin, Homer...</font>

110
00:06:46,580 --> 00:06:49,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I thought I made myself clear!</font>

111
00:06:49,750 --> 00:06:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I warned you to clean up your act
before it's too late!</font>

112
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:02,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They have done an intensely foolish thing.</font>

113
00:07:02,790 --> 00:07:05,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I deeply apologize for their insolence.</font>

114
00:07:11,210 --> 00:07:14,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Under my authority as the king of Anemone,</font>

115
00:07:14,130 --> 00:07:16,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Erwin Adonis Coronaria...</font>

116
00:07:16,500 --> 00:07:18,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Homer Adonis Coronaria...</font>

117
00:07:19,170 --> 00:07:22,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I hereby strip you both of your
royal titles and all rights therein!</font>

118
00:07:23,630 --> 00:07:24,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Arrest them!</font>

119
00:07:24,630 --> 00:07:25,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes, sir!</font>

120
00:07:27,630 --> 00:07:28,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let me go!</font>

121
00:07:29,380 --> 00:07:30,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You ruffians!</font>

122
00:07:34,420 --> 00:07:38,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Who besides me or Homer
is fit to inherit the throne, Father?!</font>

123
00:07:41,210 --> 00:07:42,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Your Majesty.</font>

124
00:07:43,170 --> 00:07:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I had a premonition.</font>

125
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I know you have
something to discuss with me.</font>

126
00:07:47,170 --> 00:07:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Or rather,</font>

127
00:07:48,290 --> 00:07:53,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">something you originally
wished to discuss with my mother, yes?</font>

128
00:07:54,380 --> 00:07:55,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's regarding...</font>

129
00:07:56,170 --> 00:08:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">the cancellation of the engagement
between Prince Leon Adonis Coronaria</font>

130
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and myself.</font>

131
00:08:02,540 --> 00:08:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Isn't that right?</font>

132
00:08:08,290 --> 00:08:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">In order to officially give Prince Leon
the right to the throne back.</font>

133
00:08:15,790 --> 00:08:16,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How did you know?!</font>

134
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:21,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Crown Princess Pride, at this time-</font>

135
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wait a moment.</font>

136
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:28,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Please,
listen to what I have to say first.</font>

137
00:08:30,540 --> 00:08:34,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">As representative of the queen,</font>

138
00:08:34,330 --> 00:08:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I formally received permission
from my mother.</font>

139
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:39,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I am here to request the
immediate dissolution</font>

140
00:08:39,830 --> 00:08:44,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">of the engagement between
Prince Leon Adonis Coronaria and myself.</font>

141
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:49,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">For that is what
the Kingdom of Freesia wishes.</font>

142
00:08:53,830 --> 00:08:55,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ridiculous!</font>

143
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:57,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Our brother is the perfect prince!</font>

144
00:08:57,670 --> 00:09:01,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There is no reason for Freesia
to want the engagement to be dissolved!</font>

145
00:09:01,380 --> 00:09:02,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He's right!</font>

146
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:04,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But there is a reason.</font>

147
00:09:04,880 --> 00:09:09,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's because the original need
for our engagement no longer exists.</font>

148
00:09:11,710 --> 00:09:13,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The engagement was first proposed</font>

149
00:09:13,750 --> 00:09:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">as a way to solidify the alliance
between our two kingdoms.</font>

150
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:24,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And furthermore, to put that alliance
on display for our neighboring countries.</font>

151
00:09:28,630 --> 00:09:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But I had a premonition.</font>

152
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I saw the future of the Anemone Kingdom,</font>

153
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:38,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">which fell to the verge of ruin
after Prince Leon left.</font>

154
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Prince Leon, you are someone
that this country needs.</font>

155
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:52,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If you wish to become a ruler who loves
and cherishes their citizens,</font>

156
00:09:52,420 --> 00:09:54,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">much like I do,</font>

157
00:09:54,630 --> 00:09:56,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">then we shall be sworn allies.</font>

158
00:09:57,170 --> 00:09:59,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There is no need for an engagement.</font>

159
00:10:00,540 --> 00:10:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sworn allies...</font>

160
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:03,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Precisely.</font>

161
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:06,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">As long as our relationship is solid,</font>

162
00:10:06,250 --> 00:10:09,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">there should be no need
to prove our alliance.</font>

163
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The only thing we wish from the
Anemone Kingdom</font>

164
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:18,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">is to retain the equal partnership
that we've had until now!</font>

165
00:10:18,420 --> 00:10:20,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And solidify it further!</font>

166
00:10:21,330 --> 00:10:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A strong alliance that doesn't falter
in the face of a cancelled engagement.</font>

167
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:26,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There is nothing more ideal!</font>

168
00:10:26,330 --> 00:10:29,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And as the Crown Princess,
I will make sure it happens...</font>

169
00:10:31,790 --> 00:10:36,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">with my sworn ally, Prince Leon.</font>

170
00:10:40,540 --> 00:10:42,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It will happen.</font>

171
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:43,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Without fail.</font>

172
00:10:52,040 --> 00:10:53,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You'll regret this, Leon!</font>

173
00:10:53,790 --> 00:10:55,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're a joke!</font>

174
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:58,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A soulless puppet like you
can never become the king!</font>

175
00:10:58,580 --> 00:11:02,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're a dumb patsy who never realized
what Homer and I were up to!</font>

176
00:11:02,330 --> 00:11:04,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You don't have what it takes
to rule a kingdom!</font>

177
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:08,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Everything will fall apart in no time
with you in charge!</font>

178
00:11:10,130 --> 00:11:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Then you'll look back
and realize the truth!</font>

179
00:11:13,330 --> 00:11:15,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That I was the one worthy of being king!</font>

180
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:18,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm obviously superior
to a pathetic bastard like you</font>

181
00:11:18,580 --> 00:11:21,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">who can't live without being loved
by the masses!</font>

182
00:11:21,710 --> 00:11:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Shut your mouth!</font>

183
00:11:32,250 --> 00:11:33,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now you listen here.</font>

184
00:11:34,540 --> 00:11:38,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Prince Leon has all the qualities needed
to become a great king.</font>

185
00:11:39,170 --> 00:11:41,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He is not a puppet
or anything of the sort.</font>

186
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He loves his people more than himself and
strives to live up to their expectations.</font>

187
00:11:46,170 --> 00:11:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He's a vital asset who has
dedicated himself to being a worthy king.</font>

188
00:11:52,790 --> 00:11:57,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You think everything will fall apart
with him in charge?</font>

189
00:11:59,500 --> 00:12:01,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">In my premonition,</font>

190
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:05,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">that's exactly what happened after
Prince Leon left and YOU became king.</font>

191
00:12:05,790 --> 00:12:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Under your reign, the people became
so poor they had to leave the country,</font>

192
00:12:10,500 --> 00:12:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">which tanks the trade market.</font>

193
00:12:12,710 --> 00:12:15,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Things got so bad for everyone,
including the royal family,</font>

194
00:12:15,580 --> 00:12:20,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">that they could hardly believe
the Anemone Kingdom was ever prosperous.</font>

195
00:12:21,130 --> 00:12:22,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Elder Sister...</font>

196
00:12:23,330 --> 00:12:26,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And worst of all,
the instant things start looking bad,</font>

197
00:12:26,790 --> 00:12:32,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">you come to Freesia
begging for Prince Leon's help!</font>

198
00:12:33,750 --> 00:12:37,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's how things play out for them
in the game.</font>

199
00:12:38,130 --> 00:12:41,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Despite being the source
of Leon's downfall,</font>

200
00:12:41,580 --> 00:12:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">they shamelessly
come to him for help over and over.</font>

201
00:12:44,420 --> 00:12:46,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They beg him to come back.</font>

202
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:47,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And then...</font>

203
00:12:48,250 --> 00:12:50,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They have the gall to ask him:</font>

204
00:12:50,170 --> 00:12:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">"Do you not care
what happens to our people?!"</font>

205
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:58,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This infuriates Leon
who sends them packing.</font>

206
00:13:00,460 --> 00:13:03,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And then he breaks down
in Tiara's arms afterwards.</font>

207
00:13:03,040 --> 00:13:05,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's one of the most
heartbreaking scenes in the game.</font>

208
00:13:07,380 --> 00:13:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ever since his brothers were young,</font>

209
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:12,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">they harbored a sense of inferiority
towards Crown Prince Leon.</font>

210
00:13:13,630 --> 00:13:16,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's why they spread rumors about him,</font>

211
00:13:16,540 --> 00:13:21,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">which resulted in Leon being forced
to marry into the Freesian royal family.</font>

212
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:24,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">However,
the king later learned the truth...</font>

213
00:13:24,790 --> 00:13:30,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and upon deciding that Leon should be
the heir to the throne after all,</font>

214
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">he warned them:</font>

215
00:13:31,500 --> 00:13:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You best clean up your act
before it's too late!</font>

216
00:13:35,330 --> 00:13:37,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But that doesn't stop them.</font>

217
00:13:37,290 --> 00:13:41,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Determined to force Leon
out of the running for the throne,</font>

218
00:13:41,290 --> 00:13:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">they make him drink,
and drop him off at a pub.</font>

219
00:13:46,420 --> 00:13:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That alone makes them utter scumbags,
but it gets worse...</font>

220
00:13:51,830 --> 00:13:53,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You witch.</font>

221
00:13:53,540 --> 00:13:56,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Just how much
did your premonition show you?!</font>

222
00:13:56,540 --> 00:13:58,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I know all sorts of things.</font>

223
00:13:58,830 --> 00:14:04,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">For example, the fact His Majesty already
learned about your wrongdoings,</font>

224
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and told you he would make Leon
heir to the throne a few days ago.</font>

225
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Remember this.</font>

226
00:14:15,670 --> 00:14:17,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">From here on,</font>

227
00:14:17,750 --> 00:14:19,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">no matter what punishment you face...</font>

228
00:14:21,210 --> 00:14:26,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">if you ever pose a threat to this kingdom
or my sworn ally Prince Leon again,</font>

229
00:14:26,130 --> 00:14:28,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I will NOT stand for it.</font>

230
00:14:29,580 --> 00:14:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If you dare to cross that line,</font>

231
00:14:32,130 --> 00:14:38,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">then you will be making
a personal enemy of Pride Royal Ivy.</font>

232
00:14:38,790 --> 00:14:42,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And I will punish you both
with my own two hands.</font>

233
00:14:44,380 --> 00:14:48,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">As if some lucky bitch
born into a Queendom is worth anything!</font>

234
00:14:49,040 --> 00:14:52,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ignorant hooligans like you
who don't even try to understand</font>

235
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:55,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">the role and duties of royalty
are even more worthless.</font>

236
00:14:58,790 --> 00:15:02,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Leon was racked by so much grief
at the start of the game...</font>

237
00:15:03,170 --> 00:15:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">because all of the Anemonians who were in
the pub with him got sentenced to death.</font>

238
00:15:10,040 --> 00:15:17,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Made even worse by the fact
Pride ordered Leon to kill them himself.</font>

239
00:15:19,710 --> 00:15:20,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">To top it off,</font>

240
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">it was his brothers who offered
the innocent citizens to Pride</font>

241
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">as "criminals" in the first place.</font>

242
00:15:29,330 --> 00:15:34,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Soon after Leon moves to Freesia,
the king falls ill and dies,</font>

243
00:15:34,540 --> 00:15:36,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">causing his brothers
to inherit the throne.</font>

244
00:15:37,250 --> 00:15:40,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They proceed to make
an absolute mess of everything</font>

245
00:15:40,460 --> 00:15:43,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and then have the gall
to ask Leon to fix it.</font>

246
00:15:44,580 --> 00:15:50,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They pressure Tiara to help them convince
him to return to the Anemone Kingdom,</font>

247
00:15:51,500 --> 00:15:57,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and even kidnap Tiara to use as a hostage
and threaten Leon into coming back home.</font>

248
00:15:59,420 --> 00:16:01,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We all carry the duty of royalty,</font>

249
00:16:01,710 --> 00:16:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">so I can't find it in myself
to cut them any slack right now.</font>

250
00:16:05,330 --> 00:16:06,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Tell me something.</font>

251
00:16:06,920 --> 00:16:10,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What sort of vision did you have
for this kingdom after taking the throne?</font>

252
00:16:11,080 --> 00:16:15,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Because if the citizens
weren't the first thing on your mind,</font>

253
00:16:15,130 --> 00:16:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">then you're failures.</font>

254
00:16:16,920 --> 00:16:22,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You have no right to reject Leon
and his incredibly pure heart.</font>

255
00:16:29,170 --> 00:16:30,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm sorry for stepping out of line.</font>

256
00:16:36,420 --> 00:16:38,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Elder Sister, are you all right?</font>

257
00:16:39,710 --> 00:16:40,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm fine.</font>

258
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Pride...</font>

259
00:16:56,500 --> 00:16:57,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you.</font>

260
00:17:05,460 --> 00:17:08,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Prince Leon, please be proud.</font>

261
00:17:08,710 --> 00:17:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Please love. Please wish for things.</font>

262
00:17:12,250 --> 00:17:17,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Your pure heart and this country
that you love so much...</font>

263
00:17:17,420 --> 00:17:19,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's all so very beautiful.</font>

264
00:17:22,380 --> 00:17:28,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He's gone through so much suffering
these past few days because of me.</font>

265
00:17:29,210 --> 00:17:32,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Despite being tormented
by the love of his country,</font>

266
00:17:32,250 --> 00:17:35,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">he kept it all bottled inside
to maintain appearances.</font>

267
00:17:35,500 --> 00:17:38,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He played the role of sweet prince</font>

268
00:17:38,080 --> 00:17:41,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and suppressed all his true feelings
to avoid any problems.</font>

269
00:17:41,670 --> 00:17:44,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">All while smiling
and whispering words of love to me.</font>

270
00:17:46,130 --> 00:17:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But in reality, he was full of more pain
and tears than anyone.</font>

271
00:17:51,420 --> 00:17:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank goodness.</font>

272
00:17:53,170 --> 00:17:57,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm so glad I could give him
the Anemone Kingdom back.</font>

273
00:17:58,130 --> 00:18:02,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And return him to his rightful place
in the Anemone Kingdom.</font>

274
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:09,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Crown Prince Leon Adonis Coronaria.</font>

275
00:18:10,670 --> 00:18:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Do you swear,
in times of sickness and health,</font>

276
00:18:15,380 --> 00:18:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">in times of prosperity and poverty,</font>

277
00:18:18,500 --> 00:18:21,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">to love and protect
the people of your country,</font>

278
00:18:21,080 --> 00:18:24,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and make the nation better for everyone,</font>

279
00:18:25,250 --> 00:18:29,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">by ensuring they can maintain
their livelihoods?</font>

280
00:18:32,330 --> 00:18:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I do!</font>

281
00:18:39,290 --> 00:18:41,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Your Majesty King Gregorio,</font>

282
00:18:42,290 --> 00:18:45,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I have one more thing to ask of you.</font>

283
00:18:45,040 --> 00:18:47,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Allow me to introduce my younger brother</font>

284
00:18:47,460 --> 00:18:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and the knights who helped
to make this right.</font>

285
00:18:49,710 --> 00:18:53,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Please honor them
with a handshake and a greeting.</font>

286
00:18:53,750 --> 00:18:55,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Of course.</font>

287
00:18:55,000 --> 00:18:56,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I will do the same!</font>

288
00:19:15,170 --> 00:19:16,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Everything should be okay now.</font>

289
00:19:17,540 --> 00:19:19,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">In the game, the king had to make Leon</font>

290
00:19:19,750 --> 00:19:22,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">take responsibility
for the commotion at the pub</font>

291
00:19:22,790 --> 00:19:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and exiled him from the country.</font>

292
00:19:25,290 --> 00:19:29,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But as soon as Leon was sent to Freesia,
the king fell ill and passed away.</font>

293
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">However, Arthur's special ability is the
power to heal anything in creation.</font>

294
00:19:37,130 --> 00:19:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Based on the look he just gave,</font>

295
00:19:39,500 --> 00:19:43,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm sure the king's sickness
has already been healed.</font>

296
00:19:47,920 --> 00:19:49,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Princess Pride...</font>

297
00:19:51,040 --> 00:19:55,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You can keep calling me Pride
like you have up to now, Prince Leon.</font>

298
00:19:55,460 --> 00:19:57,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We are sworn allies, after all.</font>

299
00:20:02,580 --> 00:20:06,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Then, please call me Leon.</font>

300
00:20:06,080 --> 00:20:08,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'd be happier that way.</font>

301
00:20:08,750 --> 00:20:10,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">All right, Leon.</font>

302
00:20:10,880 --> 00:20:13,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I look forward to seeing you again.</font>

303
00:20:13,710 --> 00:20:15,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You do?</font>

304
00:20:15,130 --> 00:20:16,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes, I do.</font>

305
00:20:17,630 --> 00:20:18,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay.</font>

306
00:20:31,290 --> 00:20:32,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Your Highness.</font>

307
00:20:33,040 --> 00:20:34,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Go ahead.</font>

308
00:20:40,500 --> 00:20:41,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Pride...</font>

309
00:20:44,500 --> 00:20:47,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I am forever in your debt.</font>

310
00:20:47,880 --> 00:20:54,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If you or Freesia ever need anything,
the Anemone Kingdom will...</font>

311
00:20:55,460 --> 00:20:59,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No, I will come running to your aid,
no matter what.</font>

312
00:21:03,540 --> 00:21:05,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let us keep in touch.</font>

313
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I will come see you as often as needed.</font>

314
00:21:07,670 --> 00:21:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And I will be waiting for you here
in my beloved country, always.</font>

315
00:21:13,080 --> 00:21:16,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Farewell, my darling fiancée.</font>

316
00:21:25,830 --> 00:21:28,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You are my first love.</font>

317
00:21:34,080 --> 00:21:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">P-Princess Pride?!</font>

318
00:21:35,540 --> 00:21:36,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Elder Sister!</font>

319
00:21:38,170 --> 00:21:40,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">First love?!</font>

320
00:21:40,380 --> 00:21:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Pride? Me?!</font>

321
00:21:44,790 --> 00:21:46,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh jeez!</font>

322
00:21:47,250 --> 00:21:51,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's the incredible seductiveness
of the "flirt" archetype</font>

323
00:21:51,420 --> 00:21:53,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">from the first ORL game for you!</font>

